text: The One UI is a operating system used by Samsung smartphones that next to Samsung Experience, in addition to the Android operating system. == History == In November 2018, the first One UI version was started called "One UI 1" which based on Android 9. In October 2022, the One UI 5 with Android 13 was started. In 30 October 2023, the One UI 6 based on Android 14 was started. It has new features like changes in quick settings, new camera widget and new editing features. == Related pages == *Samsung Experience == References == == Other websites == * Category:Samsung Category:Computers Category:Samsung software
